To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private MeanAbsoluteDeviation _mad;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_mad = MAD(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_mad.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "mean", _mad.Mean.Current.Value);
    Plot("My Indicators", "meanabsolutedeviation", _mad.Current.Value);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.mad = self.MAD(symbol, period)

# In OnData()
if self.mad.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "mean", self.mad.Mean.Current.Value)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "meanabsolutedeviation", self.mad.Current.Value)
